dct_description_sm: published by the American Sunday School Union ... revised by the Committee of publication ; engraved by John and William W. Warr ; hills etched by F. Dankworth.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "British statute miles" and "Geographic miles".
Shows topography, drainage, travel routes, territorial boundaries of the tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
